description:
Service Usage

This service is designed to notify consumers of risk check status for a visa application. The application can have a risk as well as every associated client. The service is also designed to notify if this risk is trending up or down.
readme:
Service Usage

This service is designed to notify consumers of risk check status for a visa application. The application can have a risk as well as every associated client. The service is also designed to notify if this risk is trending up or down.

Service Behaviour

This service is published from Risk using topics and subscriped by potentially many consumers.
